{"tid":1386603,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Amazon 發夢購物指南","createTime":"2019-07-30T11:22:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T03:36:15.000Z","uid":64865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"72ecec68c5fab2916bfbd52a455453316999cd00","tid":1386603,"uid":64865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:22:06.000Z","msg":"最近搬屋，響 Amazon 買咗一 set 裝修用品返嚟，又咁啱見到咁多哥哥姐姐想幫下 d 小朋友<br />\n自己年紀都唔細，做過唔少功課，想同各位哥哥姐姐分享下<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n豬咀<br />\n<br />\n- 6500 系，雙濾頭<br />\n- 7500 系，雙濾頭，成個都係矽膠製，戴得耐舒服好多，亦無咁易敏感<br />\n<br />\n留意番最尾個位係 size，1 - small; 2 - medium; 3 - large<br />\n即係 7501 係細，7502 係中，7503 係大<br />\n3M 自己介紹 medium 已經可以包到 80% 左右人口<br />\n<br />\n我個頭比較長，所以係要買 7503<br />\n女仔可能要 small size 7501/ 6501<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n買完咀，要買濾芯，記住幾個 number 就得<br />\n<br />\n最好 60928, 60923 (P100，防 organic &amp; acid gas)<br />\n亦好 60921, 60925 (P100，防 organic gas)<br />\n都好 60926  (P100，防 multi gas)<br />\n60922 都殺 (P100 + acid gas)<br />\n<br />\n記住 60928, 60923 &gt; 60921, 60925 &gt; 60926<br />\n<br />\n介紹番一個 page，詳情可以自己研究下<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Dr.Incognito.HK/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FDr.Incognito.HK%2F&d=R3EG5gZ7WKeJnJLyvNLCub3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=adcba237\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Dr.Incognito.HK/</a><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n眼罩<br />\n<br />\n上網花多眼亂，好多唔同 spec，簡單講下有邊幾樣考慮<br />\n<br />\n如果係四眼仔 <br />\nOTG - over the glasses 即係四眼仔都岩戴<br />\n<br />\n美版 (ANSI) 同歐版 (EN166) 標準有 d 出入<br />\n<br />\n防撞擊<br />\nZ87/ Z87+ - 美版防物理，Z87+ 更實淨<br />\nEN166 A/B/F - 歐版防物理，A, B 最好<br />\n<br />\n防化學野<br />\nD3 (美) / 3 (歐) - 防水滴，水濺<br />\nD4/ 4 - 防大粒塵<br />\nD5/ 5 - 防細粒塵<br />\n<br />\n透氣<br />\nDirect ventilation - 唔需要考慮<br />\nIndirect vent - 間接透氣<br />\nNon vent - 即係密封 Sealed，最安全啦，你知屋企裝修好大塵，通常都會配埋 anti-fog 防霧<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n最後就係運費同時間<br />\n如果想快，加多大約兩舊水港紙，三四日到香港，送到府上，DHL/ UPS<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n最後就係 Wishlist，無 ref 可以放心 click<br />\n<br />\n3M 7503 大 size<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B008MCUULW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB008MCUULW&d=R3EG5gZ7WKeJnJLyvNLCub3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=b5de0a2c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B008MCUULW</a><br />\n<br />\n3M 7502 中 size<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B008MCUT86/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB008MCUT86%2F&d=R3EG5gZ7WKeJnJLyvNLCub3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=ff77a33d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B008MCUT86/</a><br />\n<br />\n60923<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B00AEFCKKY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB00AEFCKKY%2F&d=R3EG5gZ7WKeJnJLyvNLCub3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=5d3e4424\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B00AEFCKKY/</a><br />\n<br />\n眼罩有太多<br />\n可以考慮<br />\nUvex Stealth OTG<br />\nUvex Flex Seal<br />\nBolle COVERALL COVERSI<br />\nBolle ATTACK ATPSI"},{"pid":"ff1e70077d95d4b7fc44349b9b126bf422cfb836","tid":1386603,"uid":135916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:58:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"70bdb472490cc11b56ad5de7fe727a6e366110e8","tid":1386603,"uid":204247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T01:07:32.000Z","msg":"此商品無法運送至 Hong Kong。 請查看是否有其他賣家提供國際寄送服務。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"440fa15a9d0d5e9e6c087ad331eadb91c4fec252","tid":1386603,"uid":245274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:25:52.000Z","msg":"推， 3M係好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.